<div data-controller="market-comps">
<section class="min-h-screen bg-brand-50 py-24 sm:py-28" id="market-comps-tool">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <%= form_with model: Lead.new, url: leads_path do |f| %>
      <%= f.hidden_field :source, value: "market_comps" %>

      <div data-market-comps-target="error" role="alert"
        class="mx-auto mb-6 hidden max-w-5xl rounded-sm border border-red-200 bg-red-50 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-red-700"></div>

      <!-- STEP 1: WEBSITE -->
      <div data-market-comps-target="websiteStep" class="mx-auto max-w-5xl text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-900 shadow-soft">
          <%= lucide_icon "sparkles", class: "h-4 w-4 text-brand-300" %>
          Market Comps Tool
        </div>

        <h1 class="mt-6 font-serif text-5xl font-medium leading-tight text-brand-900 sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
          See what similar TMT companies
          <br>
          are selling for today
        </h1>

        <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">
          Review preliminary market comps, sector multiples, pricing signals, and comparable business activity.
        </p>

        <div class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-xl rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
          <%= f.label :company_website, "Enter your company website", class: "mb-2 block text-left font-serif text-2xl font-medium text-brand-900" %>

          <%= f.url_field :company_website,
            placeholder: "Company website URL",
            data: { market_comps_target: "websiteInput" },
            class: "w-full rounded-sm border border-brand-100 px-4 py-4 text-sm text-brand-900 placeholder:text-slate-400" %>

          <button
            type="button"
            data-action="market-comps#showFinancials"
            class="mt-5 w-full rounded-sm bg-brand-900 px-6 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-white transition hover:bg-brand-500">
            Next
          </button>

          <p class="mt-4 text-center text-xs text-slate-500">
            No email required to preview. 100% confidential.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- STEP 2: FINANCIAL DATA -->
      <div data-market-comps-target="financialStep" class="mx-auto hidden max-w-6xl">
        <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-stretch">

          <div class="rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-white p-8 shadow-soft">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-6">
              <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-medium leading-tight text-brand-900">
                Now, let’s get some basic financial data
              </h2>

              <span class="font-serif text-2xl text-brand-900">2/2</span>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 border-t border-brand-100 pt-8">
              <div>
                <%= label_tag "comps_revenue", "Revenue", class: "mb-2 block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600" %>
                <%= number_field_tag "comps_revenue",
                  nil,
                  min: 0,
                  placeholder: "What were your 2025 sales?",
                  data: { market_comps_target: "revenueInput" },
                  class: "w-full rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-white px-4 py-4 text-sm text-brand-900 placeholder:text-slate-400" %>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-5">
                <%= label_tag "comps_profit", "Pre-Tax Profit", class: "mb-2 block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600" %>
                <%= number_field_tag "comps_profit",
                  nil,
                  min: 0,
                  placeholder: "What is your net profit before taxes?",
                  data: { market_comps_target: "profitInput" },
                  class: "w-full rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-white px-4 py-4 text-sm text-brand-900 placeholder:text-slate-400" %>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-5">
                <%= label_tag "comps_salary", "Owner Salary", class: "mb-2 block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600" %>
                <%= number_field_tag "comps_salary",
                  nil,
                  min: 0,
                  placeholder: "How much do you pay yourself?",
                  data: { market_comps_target: "salaryInput" },
                  class: "w-full rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-white px-4 py-4 text-sm text-brand-900 placeholder:text-slate-400" %>
              </div>

              <button
                type="button"
                data-action="market-comps#startReport"
                class="mt-8 w-full rounded-sm bg-brand-900 px-6 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-white transition hover:bg-brand-500">
                Generate Market Comps Report
              </button>

              <button
                type="button"
                data-action="market-comps#backToWebsite"
                class="mt-3 w-full rounded-sm border border-brand-100 px-6 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-brand-900 hover:bg-brand-50">
                Back
              </button>

              <p class="mt-6 text-center text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500">
                Free instant market comps. No email or sign-up necessary.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-white p-8 shadow-soft">
  <div data-market-comps-target="previewIntro" class="hidden animate-fade-up">
    <h3 class="font-serif text-4xl font-medium text-brand-900">
      <span data-market-comps-target="companyName">Your Business</span>
    </h3>

    <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-7 text-slate-600">
      Preliminary company context is being reviewed for sector comparables and market positioning.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
      <%= lucide_icon "globe", class: "h-4 w-4" %>
      www.company.com
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 border-t border-brand-100 pt-8 hidden animate-fade-up" data-market-comps-target="previewProducts">
    <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-900">Products & Services</p>

    <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <% ["software", "managed services", "telecom", "cloud", "data"].each do |tag| %>
        <span class="rounded-sm bg-brand-50 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slate-600"><%= tag %></span>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 border-t border-brand-100 pt-8 hidden animate-fade-up" data-market-comps-target="previewMarkets">
    <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-900">End Markets</p>

    <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <% ["B2B", "enterprise", "SMB", "digital infrastructure", "technology buyers"].each do |tag| %>
        <span class="rounded-sm bg-brand-50 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slate-600"><%= tag %></span>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-4">
    <div class="h-4 w-full rounded-full bg-slate-200"></div>
    <div class="h-4 w-10/12 rounded-full bg-slate-200"></div>
    <div class="h-4 w-8/12 rounded-full bg-slate-200"></div>
    <div class="h-10 w-full rounded-sm bg-slate-200"></div>
    <div class="h-10 w-8/12 rounded-sm bg-slate-200"></div>
  </div>
</div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- STEP 3: PROCESSING -->
      <div data-market-comps-target="loadingStep" class="mx-auto hidden max-w-6xl">
        <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-stretch">

          <div class="rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-white p-8 shadow-soft">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-medium text-brand-900">
              Working on your report...
              <span data-market-comps-target="progressText" class="float-right">0%</span>
            </h2>

            <div class="mt-6 h-3 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-brand-50">
              <div data-market-comps-target="progressBar" class="h-full w-0 rounded-full bg-brand-300 transition-all duration-300"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8">
              <p data-market-comps-target="loadingTitle" class="font-bold text-brand-900">
                Analyzing website data
              </p>

              <p data-market-comps-target="loadingDescription" class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
                Reviewing business model and company signals.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div data-market-comps-target="stepList" class="mt-8 space-y-3"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-white p-8 shadow-soft">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-4xl font-medium text-brand-900">
              <span data-market-comps-target="companyName">Your Business</span>
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-7 text-slate-600" data-market-comps-target="previewSummary">
              Preliminary company context is being reviewed for sector comparables and market positioning.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <%= lucide_icon "globe", class: "h-4 w-4" %>
              <span data-market-comps-target="previewWebsite">www.company.com</span>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 border-t border-brand-100 pt-8">
              <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-900">Products & Services</p>

              <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3" data-market-comps-target="previewProductTags">
                <% ["software", "managed services", "telecom", "cloud", "data"].each do |tag| %>
                  <span class="rounded-sm bg-brand-50 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slate-600"><%= tag %></span>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 border-t border-brand-100 pt-8">
              <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-900">End Markets</p>

              <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3" data-market-comps-target="previewMarketTags">
                <% ["B2B", "enterprise", "SMB", "digital infrastructure", "technology buyers"].each do |tag| %>
                  <span class="rounded-sm bg-brand-50 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slate-600"><%= tag %></span>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- STEP 4: REPORT -->
      <div data-market-comps-target="reportStep" class="mx-auto hidden max-w-6xl">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-medium text-brand-900">
          Your industry comparables report is ready!
        </h2>

        <!-- Snapshot Cards -->
        <div class="mt-6 rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600" data-market-comps-target="sectorLabel">
            Computer Systems Design and Related Services sector M&A snapshot
          </p>

          <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
            <div class="rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-brand-50 p-5 text-center">
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Comparable Deals</p>
              <p class="mt-2 font-serif text-3xl font-medium text-brand-900" data-market-comps-target="listingsCount">418</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-brand-50 p-5 text-center">
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Combined Value</p>
              <p class="mt-2 font-serif text-3xl font-medium text-brand-900" data-market-comps-target="combinedValue">$649.8M</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-brand-50 p-5 text-center">
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Median Price/Revenue</p>
              <p class="mt-2 font-serif text-3xl font-medium text-brand-900" data-market-comps-target="medianPriceRevenue">1.3×</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-brand-50 p-5 text-center">
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Median Price/Cash Flow</p>
              <p class="mt-2 font-serif text-3xl font-medium text-brand-900" data-market-comps-target="medianPriceCashFlow">3.5×</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-5 rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-brand-50 p-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
            <strong class="text-brand-900">What this means for you:</strong>
            <span data-market-comps-target="takeaway">There are active buyers and listings in your sector, with pricing signals based on revenue and cash flow multiples.</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Market Section -->
        <div class="mt-8 rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-900">What’s Hot on the Market</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Compare top business specialties and what sellers are asking today.</p>

          <div class="mt-6 overflow-hidden rounded-sm border border-brand-100">
            <table class="w-full text-left text-sm">
              <thead class="bg-brand-50 text-slate-600">
                <tr>
                  <th class="p-4">Specialty</th>
                  <th class="p-4">% of Total</th>
                  <th class="p-4">Median P/CF</th>
                  <th class="p-4">Median Asking</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>

              <tbody data-market-comps-target="specialtyRows">
                <tr class="border-t border-brand-100">
                  <td class="p-4">Computer Systems Design and Related Services</td>
                  <td class="p-4">100%</td>
                  <td class="p-4">3.5×</td>
                  <td class="p-4">$650K</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Listings -->
        <div class="mt-8 rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-900">Relevant Listings in Your Space</h3>

          <div class="mt-6 grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-2" data-market-comps-target="listings">
            <% [
              ["Loyalty SaaS Platform", "$702K", "$642K", "$642K"],
              ["Shopify SaaS Apps", "$702K", "$642K", "$642K"]
            ].each do |name, revenue, ebitda, cash_flow| %>

              <div class="rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-brand-50 p-5">
                <h4 class="font-serif text-2xl font-medium text-brand-900"><%= name %></h4>

                <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
                  SaaS company offering proprietary software with recurring revenue and strong buyer interest.
                </p>

                <div class="mt-5 grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-sm">
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-slate-500">Revenue</p>
                    <p class="font-bold text-brand-900"><%= revenue %></p>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-slate-500">EBITDA</p>
                    <p class="font-bold text-brand-900"><%= ebitda %></p>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-slate-500">Cash Flow</p>
                    <p class="font-bold text-brand-900"><%= cash_flow %></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Methodology & sources -->
        <div class="mt-8 rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-brand-50 p-6 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
          <p class="font-semibold text-brand-900">Where these comps come from</p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Median multiples are drawn from comparable transactions in our dataset, sourced from public
            2025 broker &amp; marketplace data (as of <span data-market-comps-target="compsAsOf">2025</span>):
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1.5" data-market-comps-target="compsSources">
            <li class="text-slate-500">Sources load with your report.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
            Each comp is a directional benchmark, not a formal valuation. Final value depends on diligence,
            recurring-revenue quality, margins, customer concentration, deal terms, and timing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Form -->
        <div class="mt-8 rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl font-medium text-brand-900">
            Every strong exit starts with expert guidance
          </h3>

          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
            Connect with an AcquireTMT advisor to fine-tune your valuation and compare your company against relevant market comps.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-6 rounded-sm bg-brand-900 p-7 text-white">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-300">
              Claim your free M&A expert session
            </p>

            <h4 class="mt-3 font-serif text-3xl font-medium">
              Take the first step today.
            </h4>

            <div class="mt-5 space-y-3">
              <%= f.text_field :first_name, placeholder: "Full Name", class: "w-full rounded-sm border border-white/10 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-brand-900 placeholder:text-slate-400" %>
              <%= f.email_field :email, placeholder: "Email Address", class: "w-full rounded-sm border border-white/10 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-brand-900 placeholder:text-slate-400" %>
              <%= f.telephone_field :phone, placeholder: "Mobile Number", class: "w-full rounded-sm border border-white/10 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-brand-900 placeholder:text-slate-400" %>

              <%= f.select :message,
                ["When are you looking to sell?", "Immediately", "3-6 months", "6-12 months", "Just exploring"],
                {},
                class: "w-full rounded-sm border border-white/10 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-brand-900" %>

              <%= f.submit "Book 15 minute call",
                class: "w-full rounded-sm bg-brand-300 px-6 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-brand-900 hover:bg-white" %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    <% end %>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-28" data-controller="carousel">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-medium text-brand-900 sm:text-5xl">
          What you’ll get
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-5 flex gap-2">
          <button
            type="button"
            data-action="carousel#scrollLeft"
            class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-brand-100 text-brand-900 transition hover:bg-brand-50">
            <%= lucide_icon "chevron-left", class: "h-4 w-4" %>
          </button>

          <button
            type="button"
            data-action="carousel#scrollRight"
            class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-brand-100 text-brand-900 transition hover:bg-brand-50">
            <%= lucide_icon "chevron-right", class: "h-4 w-4" %>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-md">
        <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
          A detailed and personalized market comps report.

Produced in less than 60 seconds.
        </p>

        <a href="#market-comps-tool"
          class="mt-5 inline-flex rounded-sm bg-brand-900 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white transition hover:bg-brand-500">
          Generate a market comps report
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Carousel -->
    <div class="mt-14">

      <div
  data-carousel-target="track"
  class="flex cursor-grab snap-x snap-mandatory gap-6 overflow-x-auto scroll-smooth pb-4 active:cursor-grabbing [-ms-overflow-style:none] [scrollbar-width:none] [&::-webkit-scrollbar]:hidden">

        <% [
          [
            "AI-powered valuation based on market data",
            "Get an instant valuation based on recent M&A transactions and market signals.",
            "valuation-card-1.png",
            "chart-column"
          ],
          [
            "Data-backed snapshot of your market position",
            "Quickly see how your business compares to competitors.",
            "valuation-card-2.png",
            "chart-scatter"
          ],
          [
            "Personalized valuation insights for your business",
            "Understand what specific factors may increase or reduce your valuation.",
            "valuation-card-3.png",
            "trending-up"
          ],
          [
            "Market sector valuation benchmarks",
            "Review what owners in your category are asking and selling for.",
            "valuation-card-4.png",
            "chart-bar"
          ],
          [
            "Comparable M&A transaction signals",
            "Preview relevant transaction patterns and pricing benchmarks.",
            "valuation-card-5.png",
            "briefcase-business"
          ]
        ].each do |title, description, image, icon| %>

          <div data-carousel-card class="min-w-[88%] sm:min-w-[48%] lg:min-w-[31%] snap-start overflow-hidden rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-brand-50 transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-soft">

            <!-- Top -->
            <div class="p-7">
              <%= lucide_icon icon,
                class: "h-6 w-6 text-brand-900" %>

              <h3 class="mt-5 font-serif text-3xl font-medium leading-tight text-brand-900">
                <%= title %>
              </h3>
            </div>

            <!-- Image -->
            <div class="px-7">
              <%= image_tag image,
                class: "h-72 w-full rounded-sm object-contain",
                alt: title %>
            </div>

            <!-- Bottom -->
            <div class="p-7">
              <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
                <%= description %>
              </p>
            </div>

          </div>

        <% end %>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
<section class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="rounded-sm bg-brand-900 p-8 text-white shadow-soft sm:p-10">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-medium text-white">
        Generate a market comps report
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <input
  type="url"
  placeholder="Company website URL"
  data-market-comps-target="ctaWebsiteInput"
  class="flex-1 rounded-sm border border-white/10 bg-white px-5 py-4 text-sm text-brand-900 placeholder:text-slate-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-300">
        <button
  type="button"
  data-action="click->market-comps#startFromCta"
  class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm bg-brand-300 px-8 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-brand-900 transition hover:bg-white">
  Generate Comps
</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="bg-brand-50 py-24 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-medium text-brand-900 sm:text-5xl">
      Valuation FAQ
    </h2>

    <div class="mt-12 divide-y divide-brand-100 border-y border-brand-100">
  <% [
  [
    "What should I do once I have my comps?",
    "Use your comps to stress-test your expected valuation, prepare for buyer questions, and identify value-boosting improvements before going to market. If you want deeper insight into how buyers may view your business, you can book a free 15-minute call with an AcquireTMT advisor."
  ],
  [
    "What are comps and why do they matter?",
    "Comps are comparable transactions, listings, or market benchmarks from businesses similar to yours in size, sector, and profile. They help show what the market may be paying for companies like yours and give you a stronger pricing anchor when evaluating buyer interest."
  ],
  [
    "Where does the data come from?",
    "AcquireTMT uses market intelligence, comparable M&A activity, buyer demand signals, and transaction benchmarks across technology, media, telecom, digital infrastructure, SaaS, MSP, and tech-enabled services businesses."
  ],
  [
    "Why show both price-to-revenue and price-to-cash-flow multiples?",
    "Buyers evaluate businesses through different lenses. Some TMT businesses are valued mainly on cash flow, while high-growth or recurring-revenue companies may also be assessed using revenue multiples. Showing both gives you a clearer view of the potential pricing corridor."
  ],
  [
    "How accurate are these comparable listings?",
    "Each comp should be treated as a directional benchmark, not a final valuation. Final value can change based on diligence, buyer demand, recurring revenue quality, margins, customer concentration, deal terms, and timing."
  ]
].each do |question, answer| %>
  <details class="group py-6">
    <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-medium text-brand-900">
        <%= question %>
      </h3>

      <span class="shrink-0 transition group-open:rotate-45">
        <%= lucide_icon "plus", class: "h-5 w-5 text-brand-900" %>
      </span>
    </summary>

    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base leading-8 text-slate-600">
      <%= answer %>
    </p>
  </details>

  <% end %>
</div>
  </div>
</section>
